metadata.description: This is the segmented H&E image for patientid='S13-94 A1-24' from [1,2], with a diagnosis of DCIS(grade=2). The current version includes nuclear morphometric parameters. For updated versions of this data, please see http://MultiCellDS.org [1] Dong F, Irshad H et al., Computational Pathology to Discriminate Benign from Malignant Intraductal Proliferations of the Breast. PLOS One (2014) [2] Dong F, Irshad H et al., Data from: Computational pathology to discriminate benign from malignant intraductal proliferations of the breast. Dryad Digital Repository (2014).
